      # Reading Plus SeeReader Hack
      Updated April 5, 2018.
      This tool allows you to save the story you're reading so you can
      get back to it while answering the questions.

      ## Instructions

      **THIS IS ONLY TESTED ON CHROME. USE GOOGLE CHROME!**

