      2. When you're on a SeeReader passage, there will be a variety of sections to it (usually 3-5 sections). 
         *You can view how many exist by *PAUSING* the passage and looking at the box in the bottom center.* 
         
         ![This passage contains 4 sections](https://i.imgur.com/a4MAa7Q.png)

      3. For each section, **CLICK** the bookmark *ONCE*. 
         Below the passage should appear a block of text with the title. 
         It should look like this: 
         
         ![](https://i.imgur.com/VW4vJXH.png)

      4. Every time you reach a new section, click the bookmark.
         Repeat until the story is over.


      
